s:\n   - Assume Python 3.10+. Confirm or specify a different version.\n\nIf you confirm the above resolutions, I will implement exchange (decision logic: evens_in_lst2 >= odds_in_lst1), add exchange_strict to demonstrate raising behavior, include a minimal test harness under __main__, and simulate writing the file at the requested path.'}}]
